%N A015074 Inverse of 1065th cyclotomic polynomial.
%C A015074 Periodic with period length 1065. - _Ray Chandler_, Apr 07 2017
%H A015074 Ray Chandler, <a href="/A015074/b015074.txt">Table of n, a(n) for n = 0..2000</a>
%H A015074 <a href="/index/Per#periodic">Index entries for periodic sequences</a>, period 1065.
